title: No harvest fee ever
body:
Seeing upcoming proposals to introduce different kind of fees for unstaking, harvesting or flipping, I want to make a proposal to never add these fees ever.
The worth of the token lives strongly on the abillity to compound. Fees on these actions of some kind would make compounding unefficent. This would make a lot of people (myself included) leave CAKE for other projects.
The idea of crypto has been to move from banks and their unnecessary fees. Moving your own money should not cost fees, just because this would increase value of the token.
author: 0x05151CB1b6793EA53208cFF91Cd19aBB43D20B83
